Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再那麼說 綾音她給我化的妝會...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3秒 等我3秒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 我對你的第一印象就很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是對我微笑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在入學典禮之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為我指路的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們進了同一個班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我再也沒見過像那時候的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很在意 你是什麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:21:04.42,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,banner;28;0;60,翻譯 瑤瑤 老虎 時間 校譯 阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本以為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他早忘了我們一次見面的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你一定是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實比我想像中還要好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要好?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以認為他覺得「我不錯」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又變化這麼大 讓我大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 沒想到嚇到您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不是的 不是那個意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 別問了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去排隊參拜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就是新年了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變了哦 變好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我改變了 也許真的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見到胡桃的時候不是想過要變得可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼想要變可愛 自己好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音 答案只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的變化讓我的心情好糾結
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:05:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我想的要可愛太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前那個「想要成為風早同學那樣的人」的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在卻希望「風早同學能覺得我有點可愛」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼 要持續到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道 城對矢野她厭倦為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 回去了 再見啊 城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦 龍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城 你的羽絨服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯吧 不久前新買的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概被火星燒了很多洞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 不拜神社了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易到這了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都沒和他好好解釋就把他抓來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快去快去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下次請你吃拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 不用了 會胖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.37,0:06:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好貴啊 但是 就剩我們倆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍 幹嗎啊 一個人就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 太傻了 不想待在這了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的那麼認真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是能更活潑點多好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 試著叫我「千」試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑著多好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管黑沼遇到什麼事或者遇到熟人 翔太都會搞定的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管他們了 你管的太寬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家也想看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 根本不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進展的好像很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我喝了甜酒就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在開什麼玩笑 你要陪我去拜神社
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5 4 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請你多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是新年...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有短信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 有短信 2條
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}發信人 吉田千鶴 主題 給爽子 新（年）快（樂）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}發信人 矢野綾音 主題 爽子收 今年也請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小千和綾音發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回復嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 年...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短信也被搶先了啊 不過 算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你們的福我很開心 謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子回短信了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年全是「出生以來沒有遇到過的」經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼 到我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了很多經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為遇到了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不會忘懷的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很滑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥說他元旦回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒記住人家的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家叫小遙吧 你認真一點啦 那可是要成為你嫂子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍 如果你要是遇到什麼傷心事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去安慰你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時候就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去抽籤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有心想事成之運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切記性急 請謹慎行事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇事請冷靜的與他人商量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能辦到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:12:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是小吉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待過頭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢 我最近太貪得無厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼 你是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}戀愛運 現在的這個人是最好的 不要迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是凶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說凶反而是運氣好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很少見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的是要繫在樹上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.07,0:12:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早的大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像要把風早同學的運氣都吸光了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係哦 就算吸光了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我運氣很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我想給你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說作為生日禮物是寒酸了點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的會有「迷惘」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初為什麼會煩惱這是不是戀愛之情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:14:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不明白 為什麼只是把風做同學當做是一種憧憬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和綾音兩人獨處一起過年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了讓你在篝火那等著的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 真是抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 現在是關鍵時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的笨兒子真是沒藥救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼丟人 不給你壓歲錢了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 請務必把我和城一起度過新年的事實徹底清除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這一個願望 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似進展的不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也去抽根簽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 那樣子看來真像普通的男女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話真是多啊 不是說不要了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼嘛 不就是去喝喝酒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋真是多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候有徹在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能用超隨便的說法搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙居然說年三十要去女朋友家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結什麼婚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看那人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 你一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你真是很可愛啊 經常被人這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我郵件地址吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對戴眼鏡的男生有什麼看法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下輩子再一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太囂張了 居然被搭訕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說剛才的白癡是你麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要跟過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對小P孩沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩人 別跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂叫 我要回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:16:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丟人 快離我遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登上這條坡道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是平時上學走的路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是和黑沼第一次相遇的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年會是怎麼樣的一年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 能看到那個空房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那裡也會出現哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 會出現什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別扔下我一個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 胡桃 許了什麼願
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一點點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薯片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起過年 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說就我們這些人再去歡樂下麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你表情下流哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子 還不回來麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來 很甜的哦 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很甜誒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再來一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就下次見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝 今天很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:20:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性急 我能克制的住麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒信心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛運
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉獻你的愛 就會幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同級生 旁邊座位上的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好像不僅是「朋友」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比朋友更遙遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比朋友更加貪得無厭的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.22,0:22:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的人
